{"tid":800930,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱發現咗啲好神奇嘅嘢","createTime":"2018-08-31T08:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T18:31:28.000Z","uid":141589,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d3100c9f4709860a8f1876c6c314f011ff0b2d","tid":800930,"uid":141589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"話說我有對藍芽嘅隔音耳機, bose qc 35 ii<br />\n佢可以駁3.5頭落電腦嘅 咁今朝我如常開電腦煲下劇咁 但戴咗耳機一陣發覺有啲雀仔叫聲同輕微嘅海浪聲 <br />\n利申我係check過哂冇開任何聲, volume mixer都冇顯示有聲<br />\n但我除咗個耳機又聽唔到嗰啲聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟係咩令到我聽到嗰啲聲？佢俾我感覺係喺外面經我耳機傳入嚟嘅 但又解釋唔到點樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇開錯台"},{"pid":"4d689372aca31363530b51436147a7d94388a400","tid":800930,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"咁你係咪坐海邊先"},{"pid":"7bc06916f94ff2403dbd7f9e93d8d09e8f483171","tid":800930,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"有人connect咗你個耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67a974141c53252a3f1ac99196876c75d4e970c","tid":800930,"uid":141589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d689372aca31363530b51436147a7d94388a400","tid":800930,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"咁你係咪坐海邊先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"離最近嘅海都有500米，雀仔就樓下好多"},{"pid":"f2da19f6fe3b8fcd4613f2adee71a178e61db4d2","tid":800930,"uid":2191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T18:24:22.000Z","msg":"七月啊⋯⋯真係好猛...."},{"pid":"d787f7168a42b3d2272cf64fe8a0aa9938f83b26","tid":800930,"uid":141589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"